{"tid":933781,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"計畫生育致男多女少 緬甸及越老柬女多被賣去中國","createTime":"2018-12-08T17:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-29T03:35:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5416f2e3aec4ef30280bcd4e40e04220a3ae8a54","tid":933781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T17:58:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://scd.cn.rfi.fr/sites/chinese.filesrfi/imagecache/rfi_16x9_1024_578/sites/images.rfi.fr/files/aef_image/f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fscd.cn.rfi.fr%2Fsites%2Fchinese.filesrfi%2Fimagecache%2Frfi_16x9_1024_578%2Fsites%2Fimages.rfi.fr%2Ffiles%2Faef_image%2Ff1.jpg&h=f9f52f1a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據美國一份研究調查報告，數千名來自緬甸北部的女性被賣到中國，被迫結婚生子，揭示受戰亂衝擊的邊界地帶鮮少被提及的問題。因數十年計畫生育中國各地出現男多女少現象，每年有數以萬計來自柬埔寨、老撾、緬甸和越南的女性被賣到中國。<br />\n<br />\n據法新社報道，美國發布的一分調查報告顯示，數千名來自緬甸北部的女性被賣到中國，被迫結婚生子，揭示受戰亂衝擊的邊界地帶鮮少被提及的問題。<br />\n<br />\n約翰霍普金斯大學彭博公共衛生學院（Johns Hopkins Bloomberg School of Public Health）這份報告是第一個針對此議題的研究，報告估計，7500名來自戰亂頻傳的克欽邦（Kachin）和北部撣邦（Shan）的女性淪為受害者，在中國被逼婚。<br />\n<br />\n根據成功逃回緬甸及目前仍在中國境內的多名女性訪談為基礎，報告指出，大部分被販賣到中國的女性被迫為丈夫生孩子。<br />\n<br />\n報告作者羅賓遜（W. Courtland Robinson）表示，緬甸婦女因「衝突、流離失所和貧窮」而離鄉背井，「在中國，特別是鄉村地區男女性別失衡」，意味着很多當地人苦於找不到妻子。<br />\n<br />\n報道指來自克欽婦女組織泰國分會、在克欽邦和撣邦帶領田野研究的蒙奈利（Moon Nay Li，譯音）表示，一名婦女告訴研究人員，曾被販賣到中國3次，每一次都「被迫生孩子」。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「因為政治不安定、衝突和土地被充公，女性的安危成了巨大挑戰。」<br />\n<br />\n據報道引述報告說，中國實施長達數十年的一胎化政策，導致女性人數比男性少將近3300萬人。為了填補缺口，每年有數以萬計來自柬埔寨、寮國、緬甸和越南的女性，被販賣到中國當「新娘」。<br />\n<br />\n她們中間有些人是自願前往，有些則是被欺騙或被販賣。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20181208-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%82%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%A4%9A%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%91-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%9A%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftrad.cn.rfi.fr%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%2F20181208-%25E8%25A8%2588%25E7%2595%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%2582%25B2%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A4%259A%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591-%25E7%25B7%25AC%25E7%2594%25B8%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25A4%259A%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B&d=a05yCaNB38qSNn1a92leK%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=fcb57b02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://trad.cn.rfi.fr/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B/20181208-%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%82%B2%E7%94%B7%E5%A4%9A%E5%A5%B3%E5%B0%91-%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E5%A5%B3%E5%A4%9A%E8%A2%AB%E8%B3%A3%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B</a>"},{"pid":"bf8e2a10ff6923844036dd721eae0f6e40ed653b","tid":933781,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:00:11.000Z","msg":"又一單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n慢慢周<br />\n<br />\n黑客<br />\n<br />\n西藏旅行法<br />\n<br />\n人口販賣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d3b0ed692106d060ebd1e11c6219abbafc1f181","tid":933781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T18:48:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff0580f84bf101241f7a55bb10cf490896596ba","tid":933781,"uid":35430,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T03:56:51.000Z","msg":"幾時會核清洗支那"},{"pid":"93f7ea289154b8fe738931d24f7b6e6ad230fe60","tid":933781,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T05:59:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ddda83366c245ac8e36c795e2795c5f3bf86dd2","tid":933781,"uid":100131,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 呢排贏國太多有趣事。<br />\n加上弱智口交部，弱智官員嘅反應，真係好睇過鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11cb903c4f36dfc5fd51ce5ad8f384b20aa45d05","tid":933781,"uid":53705,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-1